    * "should.be_derived_from<type>(instance)" and "should.not_be_derived_from<type>(instance)"
* Add container inspection / specification
    * "should.be_empty()" and "should.not_be_empty()/should.be_not_empty()"
    * "should.contain(instance)" and "should.not_contain()"
* Implement appropriate exception types

